      Why use our service

    • Self-custodial trade settlements

      Sellers can use their own non-custodial wallets to post arbitration bonds. Buyers can also use their own non-custodial wallets to buy Monero, providing greater control and eliminating the need for platform-held funds.

    • Strict no-KYC policy

      Our service adheres to a strict no-KYC policy, meaning that users are not required to undergo any KYC procedures to access and use its features.

    • Open source code

      Our source code is publicly accessible and licensed under an open-source model, ensuring transparency and allowing the community to inspect our service. View git instance

    • No personal information needed

      We are committed to ensuring your privacy and anonymity. Our service lets you create an account without having to provide any personal information such as name, address, or identification documents.

    • XMR ↔ fiat

      Buy Monero with PayPal, bank transfer, gift card, cash by mail or convert bitcoin to Monero - our platform supports any payment method.

    • Strict no-log policy

      We don't collect IP addresses, fingerprints or other tracking data. Our service prioritizes your privacy and does not employ any trackers like Google Analytics, which can compromise your personal data and online behavior.

    • No JavaScript needed

      Our service is designed to be accessible and functional without requiring JavaScript. This is more secure because JavaScript can be used to fingerprint users and track their online behavior. Switch to no-js version

    • No registration needed

      Users can buy Monero without the need to create an account, allowing for a quicker and more convenient experience while also providing increased privacy and anonymity.

    • Peer to peer trading

      Openmonero is a peer-to-peer trading platform that connects buyers and sellers directly, allowing users to exchange cryptocurrencies independently, eliminating the need for traditional middlemen or third-party brokers.

    • Session bot available

      For secure trade notifications, we suggest using Session, which offers a safe and private way to communicate (E2EE + onion routing). You can also use email and Nostr as backup options to receive notifications.

    • Escrow available

      For every transaction, OpenMonero requires the seller to post an arbitration bond to protect the buyer of Monero - so you can trade with peace of mind.

    • Sponsored ads

      Our sponsored ad program offers vendors a 50% discount on fees and ensures prominent placement at the top of our website. Sponsored ads are expected to have reliable service.

    • Import reputation

      Boost your reputation and increase your chances of getting more trades by importing your trading history from platforms like Localmonero, Paxful or other P2P sites.

We have no KYC checks - you can simply buy Monero anonymously without ID verification with PayPal, credit card, gift card, cash by mail, or convert bitcoin to Monero - our platform supports any payment method.

    OpenMonero is the best place to sell XMR - whether it's your mining rewards, Monero price arbitrage, or you simply see the value in servicing the community.
